    "Title": "Confiscate Contraband",
    "Description": "ATTN: Verified Mercenary Operators\n\nWe\u2019ve been able to trace a recent surge of contraband to an automated production facility at ~mission(Location|Address). We can\u2019t be sure how much longer the site will be up and running, so BlacJac needs someone on site to sweep through, secure the contraband, and transport it to us at ~mission(Destination|Address). Once there, you can use the administrative commodity terminal to transfer the contraband to us and collect your reward.\n\nWe haven\u2019t been able to determine what kind of hostile force will be present, but whatever you encounter, you\u2019re authorized to use lethal force as necessary. \n\nThe more contraband you manage to bring to us, the more credits you\u2019ll earn.\n\nThanks,\nLt. Aaron Riegert\n\nPrivate Contract Supervisor\nBlacJac Security, \"Protection Provided\"",
